  "prompt": "Where can I get a consistent high quality service for commercial cleaning in Bangalore?",
  "response": "For consistent, high-quality commercial cleaning services in Bangalore, consider the following reputable companies:\n\n1. **Cleanomatics**:\n   - Known for their professional and reliable services, Cleanomatics offers a wide range of cleaning solutions tailored to commercial spaces. They use eco-friendly products and have a strong reputation for maintaining high standards.\n\n2. **Spotless Facility Services**:\n   - This company specializes in commercial and industrial cleaning and is praised for their attention to detail and customer service. They offer customizable cleaning plans to suit different business needs.\n\n3. **Sristi Cleaning Services**:\n   - Sristi is well-regarded for its thorough and efficient cleaning services. They have a dedicated team that ensures quality and consistency across all their projects.\n\n4. **A1 Cleaning Services**:\n   - With a focus on professionalism and client satisfaction, A1 Cleaning Services provides high-quality cleaning for offices, retail spaces, and other commercial areas. They are known for their punctuality and thoroughness.\n\n5. **Clean India Show**:\n   - While primarily known for organizing cleaning industry events, Clean India Show also connects businesses with top-tier cleaning service providers in Bangalore, ensuring you get access to vetted and high-quality services.\n\nWhen choosing a cleaning service, consider visiting their websites, reading customer reviews, and possibly requesting quotes or demonstrations to ensure they meet your specific needs and expectations.",
